- set_page_specific_title "Update complete"

.content-wrapper

  %h2 Update complete

  %p.space.no_indent Thank you for your updates to #{@specialist.name}. We will review these changes, and they will be available on Pathways in the near future.

  - if current_user

    %p.space.no_indent In the meantime you may #{link_to "return to #{@specialist.name}'s page", @specialist, :class => 'ajax'} or #{link_to "update #{@specialist.name}'s information again", specialist_self_edit_path(@specialist, @specialist.token), :class => 'ajax'} if you wanted to make further changes.



